@NODE "ArchiveContents" "Contents of the archive."

 1. Archive contents.

The archive you recieved should contain the following files..


        Install.......................... Installation script.
        Changes.......................... Brief Work In Progress history.
        Questions.txt.................... A short questionaire.
        Docs/History.Txt ................ Development notes.
        Docs/Register.Txt ............... Short form for updates.
        Docs/StreamLineOS.Guide ......... This Documention.
        Libs/streamlineos.library........ Shared lib of routines.
        Tools/StreamLineOS2 ............. GUI executable.
        Tools/StreamLineOS2.info ........ The icon for use with WorkBench.
        Server/StreamLineOS2 ............ This is the executable.
        Server/StreamLineOS2.Info ....... The icon for use with WorkBench.


And no other files.

No other libraries/devices e.t.c. are needed, it is a stand-alone program.
@ENDNODE

