                   Now taken over by Gideon Zenz (gzenz@ixc.net)
 PPLib020......... 68020+ Optimised powerpacker.library & PPLoadSeg.
 RemCards......... Removes unneeded PCMCIA tasks/resources.
 RememberWin...... Patches CloseWindow to Call WindowToFront(ParentWindow)

I'm also the official recoder of the following...

